  <brief_title>Creatine on Bone Mass in Postmenopausal Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Trial: Effects of Creatine Supplementation on Bone Mass and Turnover and Muscle Function in Healthy Postmenopausal Women</official_title>
