  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Animal, in vitro and small-scale studies have suggested that creatine supplementation may
      augment bone mass. This clinical trial aims to investigate the effects of a 2-year creatine
      supplementation protocol on bone mass in postmenopausal women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
