  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  healthy postmenopausal women

          -  T-score at lumbar spine, or femoral neck or total femur of between -1SD and -2.5SD

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  drugs or dietary supplements that may affect bone metabolism (e.g., bisphosphonates,
             AINEs, hormone replacement therapy, calcium, vitamin D, creatine supplementation)

          -  low BMI (&lt; 18.5 Kg/m2).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
